Key Match Events: Zach Edey contributed significantly in the first half with offensive rebounds and scoring, helping the Grizzlies to a 65-59 lead before the third quarter.

Miscellaneous Highlights: Zach Edey showed progress from his debut, but his impact wasn't enough as the Grizzlies fell to the Rockets.
